        <p>"Web developer" is the umbrella term that is used to encompass the wide variety 
            of skill sets you might have in web development.They are responsible for creating and maintaining websites.</p>
            <h3>THERE ARE THREE MAIN TYPES OF WEB DEVELOPERS:</h3>
            <p>Front-end developer-A front end developer works on the client side and they
                 design the user interfaces that we see on the screen.These are the text and beautiful colors.
                They primarily use HTML,CSS and Javascript.Taking this course implies taht youre a front end developer!</p>
            <p>Back-end developer-A back end developer works on the server side to ensure that everything
                in the system is running smoothly.Backend developers use many languages. However, the primary ones 
                are Python, PHP, Ruby and Java.</p>
            <p>Full-stack developer-Full stack devlopers are proficient in both backend and frontend.</p><br>
                <h5>Others may include Web security developers, Wordpress developers and Mobile web developers</h5><br>
                <h2>ANY ONE CAN BE A WEB DEVELOPER. FOR THIS REASON THE MARKET HAS GOTTEN COMPETITIVE.
                    FOR ONE TO BE A SUCCESSFUL WEB DEVELOPER, THEIR ARE PARTICULAR SKILKLS THAT THEY NEED TO POSESS.</h2>
                    <ol>
                        <li>Patience</li>
                        <li>Creativity</li>
                        <li>Communication</li>
                        <li>Attention to detail</li>
                        <li>Logical Thinking</li>
                    </ol>
                    <ul>
                        <li>NOTE THAT THESE ARE SKILLS THAT CAN BE DEVELOPED OVER TIME</li>
                    </ul>
